reviewText: Fascinating journey through Ireland.  Great travelogue to check out the places one would like to experience visiting in the future.

I wasent sure about this DVD at first reason being there wasent much info on it! Now Im glad I did get it! Its a wonderful DVD definately worth getting! With great history & lots of info on Celtic Ireland! If your interested in this DVD I highly recommend it! Celtic Journey Through Ireland DVD Set kept my attention & is very worth it! Enjoyable to watch!
